    "scope_2_market_based": {
      "<year>": [{ "value": <number>, "unit": "<string>", "label": "<string>" }]
    },
    "scope_3": {
      "<year>": [{ "value": <number>, "unit": "<string>", "label": "<string>" }]
    }
  }
}
```

*Each `<year>` key must be a string.  
The list may contain one object (the usual case) or multiple objects if the
source provides several distinct totals for the same year.*

--------------------------------------------------------------------
EXTRACTION PROCEDURE (for the model)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Scan the document for occurrences of **Scope 1**, **Scope 2**, **Scope 3**
   together with a four‑digit year (e.g., 2019, 2020).  
2. For each occurrence, look for the nearest row / table cell that contains a
